As the only manufacturer to have three nominees in this year’s running, Toyota’s three contenders; Corolla Hatch, RAV4 and GR Supra; stood tall among a variety of candidates ranging from small city cars to large SUVs and double-cab bakkies.  READ: Driving comfort an essential notion in Citroën vehicles Toyota are delighted to have received the following three accolades
• Family category winner: Corolla Hatch 1.2T XR CVT
• Sports/Performance category winner: GR Supra 3.0T
• Overall third place: GR Supra 3.0T